Note that we implemented GSMR using the "gsmr" package.

reference
Zhu, Z. et al. (2018) Causal associations between risk factors and common diseases inferred from GWAS summary data. Nat. Commun. 9, 224 
(https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-017-02317-2)

"gsmr_md.R" helps to implement GSMR in simulations with LD correlation matrix as identity matrix.

